headline: ExchangeRight Grows REIT Pipeline with Full Subscription of All-Cash 13 DST
summary: PASADENA, Calif., October 28, 2025--ExchangeRight has announced the full subscription of Net-Leased All-Cash 13 DST, growing the acquisition pipeline for ExchangeRight’s Essential Income REIT. The $38 million debt-free portfolio provides investors with monthly distributions at a current rate of 5.20% covered entirely by in-place lease revenue. Net-Leased All-Cash 13 DST is a closed offering and is not accepting new investors.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 We Turn Down
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
